#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:1
msgid "View"
msgstr "View"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:3
msgid "作業目的に合わせた画面レイアウト（View）の変更方法に関するメニューを説明します。"
msgstr "This section describes the menu for changing the screen layout (View) to suit your workflow."

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:27
msgid "① ☑ VSync：   　垂直同期の設定　※基本はONになっています。"
msgstr "① ☑ VSync:  \nVertical sync setting. * Enabled by default."

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:30
msgid "② Scale：   　UI表示の拡大率の設定"
msgstr "② Scale:  \nUI display scaling setting"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:33
msgid "③ ☑ Always on Top：   　FCSを常に最前面に表示するか"
msgstr "③ ☑ Always on Top:  \nWhether to keep FCS always displayed in the foreground"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:36
msgid "④ Layout ▶：   　レイアウトのプリセット設定・切り替え"
msgstr "④ Layout ▶:  \nLayout preset settings and switching"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md
msgid "Layout ▶"
msgstr "Layout ▶"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:58
msgid "① Single：Singleレイアウトに切り替え"
msgstr "① Single: Switch to Single layout"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:60
msgid "② Double：Doubleレイアウトに切り替え"
msgstr "② Double: Switch to Double layout"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:62
msgid "③ Triple：Tripleレイアウトに切り替え"
msgstr "③ Triple: Switch to Triple layout"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:64
msgid ""
"④ Sample_Layout ▶：【Save current】で登録した任意のレイアウトを選択   　【Apply】：保存したレイアウトに変更"
"     　【Delete】：保存したレイアウトを削除"
msgstr ""
"④ Sample_Layout ▶: Select a custom layout registered with [Save current]  \n"
"[Apply]: Switch to the saved layout  \n"
"[Delete]: Delete the saved layout"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:68
msgid "⑤ Save current：現在のレイアウトを名前を付けて保存"
msgstr "⑤ Save current: Save the current layout with a name"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md
msgid "**① Singleレイアウト**"
msgstr "**① Single Layout**"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:82 ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:91
#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:118 ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:128
msgid "<br><br>"
msgstr "<br><br>"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md
msgid "**② Doubleレイアウト**"
msgstr "**② Double Layout**"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md
msgid "**③ Tripleレイアウト**"
msgstr "**③ Triple Layout**"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md
msgid "**レイアウトの保存方法**"
msgstr "**How to Save a Layout**"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:111
msgid ""
"1.【Save current】を押すと「Layout Registration」ウィンドウが出るので、    Layout "
"Nameにレイアウトの名前を入力し【Save】を押します。"
msgstr ""
"1\. Press [Save current] to open the \"Layout Registration\" window.  \n"
"Enter the layout name in Layout Name and press [Save]."

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:120
msgid "2.保存したレイアウトが一覧に出ます。   【Apply】：保存したレイアウトに変更   【Delete】：保存したレイアウトを削除"
msgstr "2\. The saved layout appears in the list.  \n[Apply]: Switch to the saved layout  \n[Delete]: Delete the saved layout"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:130
msgid "3.保存したレイアウトのデータは以下のパスに格納されます。"
msgstr "3\. The saved layout data is stored at the following path."

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/view.md:144
msgid "**Menu説明 目次**"
msgstr "**Menu Descriptions - Table of Contents**"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/index.md:157
msgid "[**〇File**](file.md)：Session(セッション)ファイルの管理と基本操作"
msgstr "[**- File**](file.md): Session file management and basic operations"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/index.md:159
msgid "[**〇Settings**](settings.md)：File/Settings　FCS全体の環境設定と動作オプション"
msgstr "[**- Settings**](settings.md): File/Settings - Global environment settings and behavior options for FCS"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/index.md:161
msgid "[**〇Window**](window.md)：各種ウィンドウの表示・操作ガイド"
msgstr "[**- Window**](window.md): Display and operation guide for each window"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/index.md:163
msgid "[**〇Maya**](maya.md)：Mayaの起動・連携"
msgstr "[**- Maya**](maya.md): Launching and linking with Maya"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/index.md:165
msgid "[**〇View**](view.md)：作業画面のレイアウト調整"
msgstr "[**- View**](view.md): Adjusting the workspace layout"

#: ../../06_glossary/01_Menu/index.md:167
msgid "[**〇Explore**](explore.md)：FCSからWindowsエクスプローラーのファイル参照"
msgstr "[**- Explore**](explore.md): Browsing files in Windows Explorer from FCS"

